    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Chair seats shaped like the cup of a saddle with a slight center ridge at the front edge; most often used on Windsor chairs.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
